OL,3,CNot drinking enough water causes
OL,4,Cstronger response to stress, study
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FPeople who do not drink enough water
OL,8,Fhave a stronger biological response to
OL,9,Fstress, according to a study.
OL,11,FResearchers found those who habitually
OL,12,Fdrink less release greater levels of
OL,13,Fthe stress hormone cortisol, despite
OL,14,Fnot feeling any thirstier than people
OL,15,Fwho drink more.
