OL,4,Cstronger response to stress, study
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe study, led by experts at Liverpool
OL,8,FJohn Moores University (LJMU),
OL,9,Fincluded 16 people who drank under 1.5
OL,10,Flitres of water a day, along with 16
OL,11,Fpeople who regularly met daily
OL,12,Frecommended guidelines for fluid
OL,13,Fintake.
OL,15,FEuropean Food Safety Authority
OL,16,Fguidelines recommend that men should
OL,17,Fdrink 2.5 litres of water a day while
OL,18,Fwomen should drink two litres.
OL,20,FWhat the study involved
