OL,3,CNot drinking enough water causes
OL,4,Cstronger response to stress, study
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FResearchers monitored hydration in
OL,8,Fboth groups over seven days using
OL,9,Furine and blood samples, after which
OL,10,Fthey were invited into the lab for a
OL,11,Fstress test.
OL,13,FThe test involved a job interview, for
OL,14,Fwhich each individual was given ten
OL,15,Fminutes to prepare for.
OL,17,FAfter that time, they were invited
OL,18,Finto another room where a fake camera
OL,19,Fwas set up and asked to do the
OL,20,Finterview to a panel of three people
OL,21,Fdressed in white coats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
