OL,7,FFollowing the fake interview,
OL,8,Findividuals were then asked to do a
OL,9,Fmental maths challenge which involved
OL,10,Fsubtracting numbers as fast as they
OL,11,Fcan.
OL,13,FProfessor Neil Walsh, of the LJMU
OL,14,FSchool of Sport and Exercise Sciences,
OL,15,Fdescribed the test as "really
OL,16,Fflustering".
