OL,7,FWhat is cortisol?
OL,9,FCortisol, known as the stress hormone,
OL,10,Fis produced by the adrenal glands in
OL,11,Fresponse to stress and also plays a
OL,12,Frole in immune response, metabolism
OL,13,Fand blood pressure.
OL,15,FThe team found cortisol levels were
OL,16,Fhigher in those who drank less.
